    <title>Markdown语法</title>
    <link href="https://chenmoshaoalen.github.io/20220810/Markdown%E8%AF%AD%E6%B3%95/"/>
    <id>https://chenmoshaoalen.github.io/20220810/Markdown%E8%AF%AD%E6%B3%95/</id>
    <published>2022-08-10T08:41:40.000Z</published>
    <updated>2022-08-10T15:21:12.693Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>摘要：Markdown语法的使用 <span id="more"></span></p><br><h2 id="0-创建一个-md文件"><a href="#0-创建一个-md文件" class="headerlink" title="0.创建一个.md文件"></a>0.创建一个.md文件</h2><p>最好使用带预览功能的编辑器进行编辑，比如VScode，VScode打开预览的方式是，ctrl+P，然后在搜索框中输入<code>&gt;Markdown:Open Preview to the Side</code>即可打开侧边栏预览。<br>预览效果如下：  </p><p><img src="/20220810/Markdown%E8%AF%AD%E6%B3%95/markdownpreview.png" alt="Markdown Preview"></p><h2 id="1-标题"><a href="#1-标题" class="headerlink" title="1.标题"></a>1.标题</h2><figure class="highlight clean"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># 标题<span class="number">1</span></span><br><span class="line">## 标题<span class="number">2</span></span><br><span class="line">### 标题<span class="number">3</span></span><br><span class="line">#### 标题<span class="number">4</span></span><br><span class="line">##### 标题<span class="number">5</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>效果如下：<br><img src="/20220810/Markdown%E8%AF%AD%E6%B3%95/titlepreview.png" alt="Title Preview"></p><br><h2 id="2-段落"><a href="#2-段落" class="headerlink" title="2.段落"></a>2.段落</h2><figure class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">这是第一段</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">这是第二段</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>效果如下：</p><blockquote><p>这是第一段</p><p>这是第二段</p></blockquote><br><h2 id="3-换行"><a href="#3-换行" class="headerlink" title="3.换行"></a>3.换行</h2><p>在一行的末尾加2个以上空格，再按回车<br>或者在末尾添加标签<code>&lt;br&gt;</code></p><figure class="highlight xml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">这是第一行，最后有2个空格  </span><br><span class="line">这是第二行<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">br</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">这是第三行</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>效果如下：  </p><blockquote><p>这是第一行，最后有2个空格<br>这是第二行<br><br>这是第三行</p></blockquote><br><h2 id="4-强调"><a href="#4-强调" class="headerlink" title="4.强调"></a>4.强调</h2><p>注意代码中的空格</p><h3 id="4-1文字加粗"><a href="#4-1文字加粗" class="headerlink" title="4.1文字加粗"></a>4.1文字加粗</h3><figure class="highlight asciidoc"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">加<span class="strong">**粗**</span>啦</span><br><span class="line">加 <span class="emphasis">__粗__</span> 啦  </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>效果如下：  </p><blockquote><p>加<strong>粗</strong>啦<br>加 <strong>粗</strong> 啦  </p></blockquote><br><h3 id="4-2斜体"><a href="#4-2斜体" class="headerlink" title="4.2斜体"></a>4.2斜体</h3><figure class="highlight asciidoc"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">变<span class="strong">*斜*</span>啦</span><br><span class="line">变 <span class="emphasis">_斜_</span> 啦</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>效果如下：  </p><blockquote><p>变<em>斜</em>啦<br>变 <em>斜</em> 啦</p></blockquote><br><h3 id="4-3粗体-斜体"><a href="#4-3粗体-斜体" class="headerlink" title="4.3粗体+斜体"></a>4.3粗体+斜体</h3><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">变<span class="strong">**<span class="emphasis">*粗斜*</span>**</span>啦</span><br><span class="line">变 <span class="strong">__<span class="emphasis">_粗斜_</span>__</span> 啦</span><br><span class="line">变 <span class="strong">__<span class="emphasis">*粗斜*</span>__</span> 啦</span><br><span class="line">变 <span class="emphasis">_<span class="strong">**粗斜**</span>_</span> 啦</span><br><span class="line">变 <span class="strong">**<span class="emphasis">_粗斜_</span>**</span> 啦</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>效果如下：  </p><blockquote><p>变<em><strong>粗斜</strong></em>啦<br>变 <em><strong>粗斜</strong></em> 啦<br>变 <strong><em>粗斜</em></strong> 啦<br>变 <em><strong>粗斜</strong></em> 啦<br>变 <strong><em>粗斜</em></strong> 啦  </p></blockquote><br><h2 id="5-引用"><a href="#5-引用" class="headerlink" title="5.引用"></a>5.引用</h2><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta prompt_">&gt;</span><span class="language-bash">这是一句引用</span>  </span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta prompt_"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta prompt_"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta prompt_">&gt;</span><span class="language-bash">这是一段引用</span>  </span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta prompt_">&gt;</span><span class="language-bash">这是一段引用</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta prompt_">&gt;</span><span class="language-bash"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-bash">&gt;这是一段引用</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta prompt_">&gt;</span><span class="language-bash">&gt;引用还可以嵌套</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta prompt_">&gt;</span><span class="language-bash">&gt;&gt;嵌套还可以嵌套</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta prompt_">&gt;</span><span class="language-bash"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-bash">&gt;引用里还可以放别的东西：</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta prompt_">&gt;</span><span class="language-bash">- 比如一个列表</span>  </span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta prompt_">&gt;</span><span class="language-bash"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-bash">&gt;比如一张图片（我网上随便找的头像）![比如一张图片](/20220810/Markdown语法/unnamed.jpg)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta prompt_">&gt;</span><span class="language-bash">还可以让我的字变**粗**，变***斜***</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>效果如下：</p><blockquote><p>这是一句引用  </p></blockquote><blockquote><p>这是一段引用<br>这是一段引用</p><p>这是一段引用</p><blockquote><p>引用还可以嵌套</p><blockquote><p>嵌套还可以嵌套</p></blockquote></blockquote><p>引用里还可以放别的东西：</p><ul><li>比如一个列表</li></ul><p>比如一张图片（我网上随便找的头像）<img src="/20220810/Markdown%E8%AF%AD%E6%B3%95/unnamed.jpg" alt="比如一张图片"><br>还可以让我的字变<strong>粗</strong>，变<em>斜</em></p></blockquote><br><h2 id="6-列表"><a href="#6-列表" class="headerlink" title="6.列表"></a>6.列表</h2><p>（待更新）</p>]]></content>
    
    
